# Removing Claude Code Router
- [ ] Uninstall npm package `@musistudio/claude-code-router`
- [ ] Remove `~/.claude-code-router` directory
- [ ] Disable `tengu_ccr_bridge` in `~/.claude.json`
- [ ] Kill any running `ccr` processes
- [ ] Remove any `ccr` related shell configurations (e.g. `ccr activate` in `.zshrc`)
